   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Formulation: Danish support to IDH 2021</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Formulation: Danish support to Sustainable Trade initiative (IDH) implementing their multi year plan Catalyzing Private Sector Solutions for the Sustainable Development Goals (2021).

The objective of this assignment is to assist the Ministry of Foreign Affairs with preparation of a project (grant) to support market transformation by creating sustainable industries and value chains through new business models to improve livelihoods of small holder farmers and workers and mitigate and adapt to climate change through support to IDH.

The formulation consultant will report directly to the Project Manager in the Department for Green Diplomacy (GDI) of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs (MFA) and assist with preparation of inputs for internal discussions, as well as writing, reviewing and revising project documentation.</narrative>
